e2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg" width="678" height="651" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:651,&quot;width&quot;:678,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:194053,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>事实上，丰富的住房是新加坡如此富裕的主要原因之一。</p><p>当然，新加坡拥有如此多住房的原因是该国传说中的“公共”住房政策。那里<a href="https://www.policynote.ca/singapore-housing/">不乏</a><a href="https://www.thearcadiaonline.com/what-is-hdb-housing-and-how-does-it-work/">解释者</a>，但这里是基础知识。新加坡政府拥有大部分土地，并拥有一个称为住房发展委员会（HDB）的政府机构，该机构建造了大量住房。然后，它以便宜的价格将这种住房（即年轻人）出售给了首次购房者（即年轻人）。然后谁可以自由转售。随着时间的流逝，首次购房者的折扣和政府使价格逐渐稳定地欣赏的能力的结合意味着，HDB公寓不仅是一个廉价的居住地，而且还可以作为一种财富建设的养老金系统。换句话说，在新加坡，将您的房屋用作居住的地方并利用它来建立财富之间没有矛盾！</p><p>相当了不起。</p><p>好吧，我刚才说的一部分实际上不是真的。政府实际上并没有向人们出售HDB公寓。它出售他们99年的租赁。如果租约还剩下98年的时间，那就非常接近所有权，因此，当新加坡制度启动时，它基本上是一种房屋所有权制度（实际上，称为“免费股东”或私人拥有的新加坡房屋在技术上都在技术上是在技术上。 999年租赁！）。请记住，新加坡成立于1965年，因此还没有99年的租赁时间有时间到期。但是在几十年的时间里，这将成为脖子上的巨大痛苦，因为租赁到期的人将不得不搬到新的公寓。人们现在开始考虑那天，这使租赁<a href="https://theindependent.sg/hdbs-99-year-time-bombs-are-ticking-dont-mess-around-with-them/">市场搞砸了</a>，并导致一些公寓开始贬值。</p><p>这项为期99年的租约是对新加坡政府的一项毫无意义的政策。只要政府拥有土地，如果需要重新开发旧建筑物，它总是可以使居民搬出，这基本上就像政府控制公寓协会的公寓一样。为每套公寓增加一个时间限制，这将使人们在任意日期中搬出来是不必要的额外步骤。</p><p>但是，除了这个小问题之外，新加坡的HDB系统是解决大多数其他国家的住房问题的绝对惊人解决方案。基本上，政府拥有和开发土地使其可以控制住房供应，从而产生丰富的负担得起的住房和可预测的缓慢升值。爱尔兰<a href="https://www.irishtimes.com/ireland/housing-planning/2023/03/23/irelands-housing-crisis-facts-and-figures-all-you-need-to-know/">臭名昭著的住房短缺</a>，有可能将制药业损失到新加坡（其对美国制药FDI的主要竞争对手）的风险仅仅是因为新加坡可以建造住房，而爱尔兰不能。如果我负责爱尔兰，我将拼命寻找一些模仿HDB的方式。</p><p>实际上，如果我也是美国，我会寻找模仿HDB的方法。实际上，拜登政府一直在<a href="https://finance.yahoo.com/news/biden-unveils-plan-increase-us-122815341.html">尝试通过一项试点计划</a>，这对我来说看起来很新加坡：</p><blockquote><p>拜登·哈里斯（Biden-Harris）政府最近宣布了邻里房屋税收抵免，并为选定的首次购房者提供首付援助。该计划旨在为第一代或低养老买家创造房屋所有权的途径，而这些买家也从未拥有过房屋。</p><p>国会尚未签署邻里房屋税收抵免。如果确实通过，它将分配160亿美元的资金，以建造或修复整个美国的40万本新房屋，这是根据10月16日星期一发表的白宫的一份声明。此外，该套餐将提供100亿美元的首付。援助和1亿美元来补充首次购房者。</p></blockquote><p>美国各州也应该研究这样的计划。</p><p>无论如何，值得一提的是，并非新加坡的每个人，也不是中产阶级的每个人都生活在HDB公寓中。尽管该国很小，但在郊区风格的地区很远，大部分住房都是低层和私人拥有的。其中很多看起来像这样： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg" width="1456" height="1934" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1934,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:796690,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>这不是一个庞大的牧场，上面有草坪，但它是<em>很多</em>居住空间，并有很多隐私。然而，这种结构使区域也非常密集，即使没有高层。在美国，当然可以将某种视为“缺失中间”选择。</p><h4>新加坡街头</h4><p>现在，我要说的是，有一件事让我对新加坡的城市环境感到困扰。它的布局令人惊讶地以汽车为中心。</p><p>新加坡人大多乘火车和公共汽车来四处走动； <a href="https://www.deccanherald.com/world/singapores-car-lite-policy-reduces-car-ownership-to-one-third-down-from-40-in-2013-2758732">只有三分之一</a>的人口甚至完全拥有汽车。火车系统很棒 - 不像日本那样好，但没有什么。步行很容易。</p><p>但是，当您走来走去时，您经常会在一条非常大街道的狭窄人行道上行走。例如，这里是我在小印度拍摄的照片，这是新加坡最充满活力的种族社区之一： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg" width="616" height="819" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:819,&quot;width&quot;:616,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:227078,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>主要购物街是一条巨大的四车道道路！拍摄这张照片时没有太多的交通（部分是因为我等到没有汽车阻碍射击的车），但是汽车经常通过，以至于您要吸收很多排气。</p><p>这也不是特别罕见的事。市中心的大部分地区充满了<a href="https://twitter.com/Noahpinion/status/1722158747043381359">巨大的动脉道路</a>，比上图所示的道路要大得多，而且城市的许多商店和餐馆都沿着这些道路的侧面。结果是，即使汽车的拥有量很低，但通常感觉就像新加坡是为汽车建造的城市。</p><p>实际上，美国人对这样的通道有一个词：“ Stroads”。 “斯特罗德”<a href="https://www.strongtowns.org/journal/2018/3/1/whats-a-stroad-and-why-does-it-matter">是由城市主义非营利组织强大的城镇创造的</a>，这是指宽阔的高速道路，同时也有望走路和购物。美国的街头比新加坡差，但新加坡有很多。</p><p>关于新加坡为何选择这种发展模式的理论比比皆是 - 有人说，卡车运输和物流是必要的，其他政府则说，政府优先考虑富有汽车所有者的利益。我与之交谈的人什至建议，人们认为宽阔的街道可以帮助新加坡动荡的早期历史上的防暴控制。无论如何，有一个以行人为中心的城市的大部分土地面积为汽车保留，这很奇怪。</p><p>解决此问题的方法是扩大人行道。一条狭窄的人行道的道路对于行人来说是不安全的，因为您离汽车非常近。它还使行人与汽车排气处密切接触。这不是四处走走的特别好： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg" width="512" height="680" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:680,&quot;width&quot;:512,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:113647,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>扩大这些人行道将使人们离汽车远离汽车，并允许安装栏杆和其他障碍，使人们有一种受到保护的感觉，以免受到损害的汽车。这可能需要牺牲一些交通车道，但是哦。</p><p>这是新加坡一条更友好的街道的一个很好的例子： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg" width="678" height="676" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:676,&quot;width&quot;:678,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:245446,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>如果我是新加坡政府，我的目标是赚更多这样的街道。如果他们有能力用零虫子修剪整齐的绿色植物来覆盖这座城市，那么他们有能力使街道对行人群众更愉快。</p><p>无论如何，撇开散文，如果没有，您绝对应该在某个时候访问新加坡。美妙的财富和未来派的太阳朋克建筑只是其中的两个景点 - 还有令人惊叹的食物，有趣的民族社区，可爱的景色，有趣的历史以及相当壮观的建筑风格。</p><p>只需记住不要意外带任何大麻，否则他们会<a href="https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/up-to-30-years-jail-for-possession-of-cannabis-with-roll-out-of-stricter-drug-laws-from-june">用拐杖殴打您，并将您送进监狱数十年</a>。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/singapore-urbanism?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/singapore-urbanism?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p>; 
Yes, it's possible to imagine progressive dystopias We shouldn't just worry about the means of progress, but the ends as well. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/yes-ts-possible-to-imagine-progressions https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/yes-ts-possible-to-imagine-progressionsNoah Smith Fri, 10 Nov 2023 07:52:40 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8d5d1ea-296e-471c-9aff-fcd212ef244c_936x624.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8d5d1ea-296e-471c-9aff-fcd212ef244c_936x624.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8d5d1ea-296e-471c-9aff-fcd212ef244c_936x624.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8d5d1ea-296e-471c-9aff-fcd212ef244c_936x624.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8d5d1ea-296e-471c-9aff-fcd212ef244c_936x624.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8d5d1ea-296e-471c-9aff-fcd212ef244c_936x624.jpeg" width="722" height="481.3333333333333" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c8d5d1ea-296e-471c-9aff-fcd212ef244c_936x624.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:624,&quot;width&quot;:936,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:722,&quot;bytes&quot;:135733,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8d5d1ea-296e-471c-9aff-fcd212ef244c_936x624.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8d5d1ea-296e-471c-9aff-fcd212ef244c_936x624.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8d5d1ea-296e-471c-9aff-fcd212ef244c_936x624.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8d5d1ea-296e-471c-9aff-fcd212ef244c_936x624.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption"> <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/53301297@N00">PASA47</a> ， <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/?ref=openverse">CC</a>的“<a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/53301297@N00/14486751845">唯一可持续增长是降解</a>”。</figcaption></figure></div><p>最近，一个想法一直在na。几个月前，布拉德·德隆（Brad DeLong）和我<a href="https://braddelong.substack.com/p/podcast-hexapodia-liii-rule-1-no#details">进行了一个播客</a>，在那里我们讨论了像布莱恩娜·吴（Brianna Wu），马特·伊格莱西亚斯（Matt Yglesias）和埃兹拉·克莱因（Ezra Klein）这样的中心左派人物，他们向左边的一些人推回了一些人。布拉德（Brad）从根本上讲这些推动力是关于<em>战术</em>的 - 正如他所看到的那样，布莱恩娜（Brianna），马特（Matt）和埃兹拉（Ezra）对某些进步主义者在尝试实现乌托邦的尝试并争辩采取更务实，有效的方法感到沮丧。这是漫长的传统的一部分，在这种传统中，倡导社会变革的激进主义者争论社会准备的变化。</p><p>但是，尽管我确实认为有些事情正在进行，但我不同意布拉德（Brad），这主要是倒退的目的。取而代之的是，我认为我们真正看到的是对进步主义者似乎正在为之奋斗的某些<em>目标</em>越来越不适，而不是关于变革的步伐，而是关于它的方向。当布拉德（Brad）挑战我列出反乌托邦渐进式愿景的一些例子时，我立即说了“降解”，他同意了。</p><p>无论如何，请注意我说“一些”一词。我想要的事情是许多进步的愿景，例如更大的经济平等，种族财富差距的缩小以及气候变化的逆转！如果您将这篇文章解释为说进步主义的<em>书面大型</em>项目是一个反乌托邦的项目，那么您将严重地误解了我。我也不是说保守主义比进步主义更好，或者政治权利不包含反乌托邦的视野。确实如此。</p><p>取而代之的是，我要说的是，在2010年代令人震惊的匆忙中所接受的一些大想法被误导了，应该被丢弃，以便为人类实际上想要生活的乌托邦努力。</p><p>这是四种此类愿景的列表。</p><h4>退生长</h4><p>当然，这是布拉德问题的简单答案。我写了多篇文章，详细介绍了为什么停止或逆转经济增长（过去十年中一些渐进界变得时尚的想法）是不可行的，也是不受欢迎的，这是限制人类环境影响的一种方式。首先，我认为，降解所需的生活水平的下降使其成为政治上的非标准，而所涉及的全球中央规划数量将无法实施： </p><div class="digest-post-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;nodeId&quot;:&quot;52bf6b2d-b886-46cf-8a98-7325f073a207&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;I was going to write a lengthy post explaining why &#8220;degrowth&#8221; &#8212; the idea that we need to halt economic growth in order to save the planet &#8212; is a very bad idea. But in the meantime, other people have written that post, or recorded that podcast, and done it well. These include&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;sm&quot;,&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;People are realizing that degrowth is bad&quot;,&quot;publishedBylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:8243895,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Econ blogger&quot;,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/89fd964a-586f-461a-9f5a-ea4587d45728_397x441.png&quot;,&quot;is_guest&quot;:false,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:10000}],&quot;post_date&quot;:&quot;2021-09-06T08:40:54.095Z&quot;,&quot;cover_image&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faeddab2a-6c56-4e5b-9c35-9ca0fecd86bd_1024x682.jpeg&quot;,&quot;cover_image_alt&quot;:null,&quot;canonical_url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/people-are-realizing-that-degrowth&quot;,&quot;section_name&quot;:null,&quot;id&quot;:39760555,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;newsletter&quot;,&quot;reaction_count&quot;:129,&quot;comment_count&quot;:106,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Noahpinion&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04281755-2cd6-42e5-a496-e69153abebb2_281x281.png&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}"></div><p>我还认为，解决气候变化需要增长，因为用太阳能和风能和电池代替我们的能源需要<em>大量</em>的经济产出。然后，一旦我们改用了这些能源，它们将变得如此便宜（由于学习曲线），我们实际上将比以前更高的消费更高。</p><p>在后续文章中，我批评了降解思想的研究和言论，这通常是基于意识形态动机的伪科学： </p><div class="digest-post-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;nodeId&quot;:&quot;15f58e2c-0355-411d-a35f-7e2969e03f23&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;A year and a half ago, I wrote a post entitled &#8220;People are realizing that degrowth is bad&#8221;. Around that time, the degrowth movement had started to receive a bit of attention in the U.S., as part of the general push for major action on climate change. But writers like&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;sm&quot;,&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Degrowth: We can't let it happen here!&quot;,&quot;publishedBylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:8243895,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Econ blogger&quot;,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/89fd964a-586f-461a-9f5a-ea4587d45728_397x441.png&quot;,&quot;is_guest&quot;:false,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:10000}],&quot;post_date&quot;:&quot;2023-05-24T01:54:00.942Z&quot;,&quot;cover_image&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F058020be-b262-4c24-88c2-ba3e1c8e0184_1024x681.jpeg&quot;,&quot;cover_image_alt&quot;:null,&quot;canonical_url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/degrowth-we-cant-let-it-happen-here&quot;,&quot;section_name&quot;:null,&quot;id&quot;:123140587,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;newsletter&quot;,&quot;reaction_count&quot;:201,&quot;comment_count&quot;:80,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Noahpinion&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04281755-2cd6-42e5-a496-e69153abebb2_281x281.png&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true}"></div><p>正如我在第二篇文章中所解释的那样，我将脱生物视为试图使民族衰落的尝试，这就是为什么这个想法在欧洲比美国更受欢迎的原因</p><p>我不想击败这一点，但我认为重要的是要强调未来的不愉快和不人道的未来。富裕国家的人们将被迫接受较低的生活水平，而发展中国家的人们将拥有<a href="https://brankomilanovic.substack.com/p/degrowth-solving-the-impasse-by-magical">更加微薄的未来</a>。这种情况无疑会引起怨恨，导致对授权大规模贫困的领导人的反对。在推翻降解政权之后，我们将摆动完全倾向于承诺无限资源消耗的领导者，这时环境将比以前更糟。这是一个事实，即降解将使投资绿色能源和保护环境的其他技术变得更加困难。</p><p>因此，尽管我认为我们确实需要担心增长的潜在负面后果并尽力减轻这些危害，但我认为试图使自己贫穷以拯救环境会成为我们和环境的灾难性错误。这不是任何进步的争取的事情。</p><h4>驱逐“殖民者”</h4><p>在我出生时，非殖民化的非殖民化（即，国家都从其欧洲帝国霸主获得独立的国家就已经有效地完成了。无论从道德和<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/against-hickelism">经济上来说</a>，这对世界来说都是一件非常好的事情。但是近年来，美国一些进步主义者开始谈论一种完全不同类型的“非殖民化”，这是从其祖先定居的地区驱逐“定居者殖民地”人口。</p><p> “非殖民化”的另一种含义一直在人文学术界和一些左倾的媒体和激进主义运动中越来越受欢迎，但在哈马斯于10月7日对以色列袭击以色列之后，它爆炸到了国家舞台上。在哈马斯的屠杀和强奸狂欢之后，青少年时尚作家纳吉玛·谢里夫（Najma Sharif）发布了以下推文： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1be80b0a-b5a2-4898-a77d-4fd80df00a22_375x134.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubs